      <u xml:id="q-d17d5d94-362c-e311-93c1-000bdb5cc6d5" who="R" n="1">When I left
				school, I got a job in an office, for the next forty years I did the same thing, I
				got married at twenty one, and suffered a heart attack at fifty and spent five
				months in hospital. Then I retired.</u>
